{"tid":425960,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［冷門病］有冇一型糖尿jj 打救 唔夠胰島素用 順便你問我答","createTime":"2017-10-06T07:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T12:45:33.000Z","uid":72130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cf8b7915a4c49bd04b547afaa6a6af0250efb707","tid":425960,"uid":72130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:57:38.000Z","msg":"利申同大家平時聽既糖尿病係唔同<br />\n識既應該知有分一型同二型<br />\n平時一日打4次針<br />\n今日唔小心打爛左成盒藥<br />\n又未覆診 藥房訂又要幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實個病好冷門 不過都想睇下有冇巴絲同我一樣唔好彩有呢個病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n順便你問我答先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8dc0bf07f62e4d07cff479b0c4d2bf0cc3e9750","tid":425960,"uid":21120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:01:58.000Z","msg":"篤左手指未"},{"pid":"cfef3b4f74c9efb91a2a30652e31d154c6a6bd3c","tid":425960,"uid":72130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>篤左手指未</blockquote><br />\n日日篤<br />\n宜家應該仲夠同2餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e104cf4c63c0ad6e2cb4788549b9d02bb153c6e6","tid":425960,"uid":99322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:05:30.000Z","msg":"一型係點先會有?<br />\n遺傳?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e428f9eedea0bfad0f82b8d2dbc4b2a35bf779","tid":425960,"uid":72130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一型係點先會有?<br />\n遺傳?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n醫學上話解釋唔到<br />\n只係顯示多數係遺傳<br />\n但我屋企人都冇<br />\n醫生話應該係我唔好彩<br />\n大約幾萬人有一個唔係遺傳先有呢個病"},{"pid":"43c7a9ace63694b54293e8377d70eb15536821b0","tid":425960,"uid":91884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一型係點先會有?<b